, the Biden Administration has now put thousands of union workers out of work. For the average American family, it means energy costs will go up and communities will no longer see the local investments that come with pipeline construction.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>But the problem is that the union endorsed Biden last year and repeatedly promoted his agenda</strong>:"},{"pid":"ced33e3104696d1dd951c9a182c1c43481661788","tid":2380291,"uid":88134,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:30:38.000Z","msg":"邊會有資本家支持既左派架講真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8b43ee672fdaaf415fdb36d1695d98f006e2fa","tid":2380291,"uid":26770,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"ced33e3104696d1dd951c9a182c1c43481661788","tid":2380291,"uid":88134,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:30:38.000Z","msg":"邊會有資本家支持既左派架講真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:34:16.000Z","msg":"關鍵係成班普通打工仔幫CHINA JOE身後跨國企業護教<br />\n未夠48小時比人賣左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"462272878bfbc6404c52dc42cbde87d10ff06140","tid":2380291,"uid":88134,"like":65,"dislike":5,"score":60,"quote":{"pid":"7e8b43ee672fdaaf415fdb36d1695d98f006e2fa","tid":2380291,"uid":26770,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"quote":{"pid":"ced33e3104696d1dd951c9a182c1c43481661788","tid":2380291,"uid":88134,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:30:38.000Z","msg":"邊會有資本家支持既左派架講真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:34:16.000Z","msg":"關鍵係成班普通打工仔幫CHINA JOE身後跨國企業護教<br />\n未夠48小時比人賣左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T18:35:37.000Z","msg